   "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
   "body" : "A few ideas for modernizing the layout as we're creating a new `guix.sigs` repo:\r\n\r\n1. Instead of having `.sig` files, just sign the commit! We can include a script with verifies that no one is signing changes to others' trees\r\n2. Hierarchy would look something like: `guix.sigs/$TAG/$HOST(-codesigned)/$SIGNER/SHA256SUMS`\r\n3. We can move `contrib/gitian-keys` to this new `guix.sigs` repo\r\n\r\nThese are just some initial ideas, please let me know if this sounds reasonable without bike-shedding ð¬  \r\n",
